a flight attendant because an Ultra-Orthodox passenger didn&#8217;t want to sit next to a woman. \u00a0Faiqa retells her similar experience when traveling to Pakistan as a teen.<\/p>\n<p>Please ensure that your tray-tables are in their upright and locked position before listening to today&#8217;s episode.<\/p>\n<p>And as always &#8211; we&#8217;d love to hear from you! Find us on <a href=\"http:\/\/www.facebook.com\/HeyThatsMyHummus\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook<\/a> or <a href=\"http:\/\/www.twitter.com\/ThatsMyHummus\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Music Credits:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Title Theme (Intro and Outtro): \u00a0 \u00a0<em>Perfect One<\/em>\u00a0(<a href=\"http:\/\/freemusicarchive.org\/music\/manbitesdog\/\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\">Man Bites Dog<\/a>) \/\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/creativecommons.org\/licenses\/by-sa\/3.0\/\" rel=\"license\">CC BY-SA 3.0<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Interstitial Music: \u00a0<em>They Don&#8217;t Make Your Kind No More<\/em> (<a href=\"http:\/\/freemusicarchive.org\/music\/The_New_Valleys\/\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\">The New Valleys<\/a>) \/ <a href=\"http:\/\/creativecommons.org\/licenses\/by\/4.0\/\" rel=\"license\">CC BY 4.0<\/a><\/p>\n<div class=\"powerpress_player\" id=\"powerpress_player_3504\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement('audio');<\/script><![endif]-->\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-1022-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio\/mpeg\" src=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/p\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-079.mp3?_=1\" \/><a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/p\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-079.mp3\">http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/p\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-079.mp3<\/a><\/audio><\/div><p class=\"powerpress_links powerpress_links_mp3\">Podcast: <a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/p\/www.heytha